<plot>A parody of anthropology, linguistics, and cultural imperialism. The film follows an unlikely team of linguists into the wilds of an ersatz Patagonia to study the last speakers of a dying language. That language apparently consists of a single word, which therefore means everything.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?237633</url></doc>
